data.description: This Bay Colony home has great curb appeal plus a spacious layout with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms plus rare gameroom and media upstairs. Lowest price per foot in the neighborhood! The home's interior boasts hardwood floors that adds warmth and elegance to the living spaces. The kitchen features modern appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage, making it a dream for aspiring chefs and avid entertainers. Two full bedrooms and bathrooms down offer a great option for a mother-in-law suite or makes for a great nursery/home office. Upstairs another two bedrooms with a jack-and jill bathroom, plus half bath and gameroom/media. Located in the desirable Bay Colony community in Dickinson with great amenities- pool, parks and walking trails, plus, this home not only offers a fantastic location near shopping but also provides access to excellent schools, parks, and recreational facilities. Near NASA, UTMB and I-45.
